PhysicalTable.name: SAMP_REVENUE_CURR_F
PhysicalTable.Description: Reveue Currency Fact table: Stores the converted fact information in different currencies.

PhysicalColumn.name: Shipto_Addr_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Shipto Address Key: Joins to Address_Key column of Addresses dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Cust_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Customer Key: Joins to Cust_Key of Customers dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Revenue_Usd
PhysicalColumn.Description: Revenue: Stores revenue converted to US Dollars as a double.

PhysicalColumn.name: Order_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Order Number: Uniquely identifies each record in the fact table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Bill_Day_Dt
PhysicalColumn.Description: Bill Day Date: Joins to Calendar_date of Time dimension table (Day grain).

PhysicalColumn.name: Prod_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Product Key: Joins to Prod_Key of Products dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Empl_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Employee Key: Joins to Empl_Key of Employees dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Bill_Mth_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Bill Month Key: Joins to Mth_Key of Time dimension table (Mth grain).

PhysicalColumn.name: Revenue_Eur
PhysicalColumn.Description: Revenue: Stores revenue converted to Euros as a double.

PhysicalColumn.name: Bill_Qtr_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Bill Quarter Key: Joins to Qtr_Key of Time dimension table (Qtr grain).

PhysicalColumn.name: Revenue_Aud
PhysicalColumn.Description: Revenue: Stores revenue converted to Australian Dollars as a double.

PhysicalColumn.name: Office_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Office Key: Joins to Office_Key of Employees dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Currency
PhysicalColumn.Description: Currency: Stores currency information like AUD, USD, EUR..

PhysicalColumn.name: Revenue
PhysicalColumn.Description: Revenue: Stores revenue information as a double.
